Initial Investigation

We have observed an alert in Splunk logs indicating that our database server is unable to connect to the application server. There could be multiple reasons for this issue.

Actions Taken

Incident Raised: We have raised an incident with the database team for further investigation.

Vendor Support: A support ticket has been raised with the Bitbucket vendor to analyze potential causes. All relevant support bundles and files have been attached to the ticket for reference.


New Relic Investigation

All utilization levels are within the defined threshold.

No signs of high resource utilization were observed from the New Relic monitoring data.


Further updates will be provided based on the ongoing investigations.

